ActDivorce Act
SubjectAlberta - Child support service
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Justice, on behalf of the Government of Canada, enter into the MEMORANDUM OF AGREEMENT between Canada and the Province of ALBERTA for the purpose of designating the "CHILD SUPPORT RECALCULATION PROGRAM" as a provincial child support service in accordance with section 25.1 of the Divorce Act.
